OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FAs we sat in our seats for the
OL,8,Finterview, the mother who must to
OL,9,Fremain anonymous to protect the
OL,10,Fidentity of her young child, seemed
OL,11,Fmore relaxed than I anticipated.
OL,13,FHer attitude was very focused, as if
OL,14,Fshe'd heard the worst evidence now the
OL,15,Ftrial was over and was determined to
OL,16,Fmake people understand the impact of
OL,17,FBennett's crimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
