OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThe mother, whom we're calling Sarah,
OL,8,Fwas one of the first people to raise
OL,9,Fconcerns to nursery staff after
OL,10,Fnoticing Nathan Bennet was overly
OL,11,Faffectionate with her child.
OL,13,FHer child was not one of Bennett's
OL,14,Fvictims, but they were cared for by
OL,15,FBennett for about five months while at
OL,16,FPartou Kings Street Nursery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
