OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773756670
OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FSarah says: "I immediately noticed
OL,8,Fthat he was extremely affectionate
OL,9,Ftouchy-feely with my child and it
OL,10,Freally stood out because it was
OL,11,Fbehaviour which was very different to
OL,12,Fhow every other member of staff in the
OL,13,Fnursery or anywhere had interacted
OL,14,Fwith my child.
OL,26,@oD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
