SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773756670
OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"It was bizarre and it really stood
OL,8,Fout to me because it was more how you
OL,9,Fwould interact with a member of your
OL,10,Ffamily you know, if my child's uncles
OL,11,For grandparents had been interacting
OL,12,Flike that with him, it would be normal
OL,13,Fand acceptable - it was very odd for
OL,14,Fsomeone who was meant to be his key
OL,15,Fworker at a nursery."
OL,17,FDuring the trial the 30 year old was
OL,18,Fdescribed as an evil predator. A man
OL,19,Fwho obsessed over some children and
OL,20,Fmade them attached to him.
OL,26,@wD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
