OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThe judge described how one child,
OL,8,Fknown to be very sociable and chatty,
OL,9,Fchanged once under Bennett's care. The
OL,10,Fchild became quiet and would only want
OL,11,Fto speak to Bennett and would wait for
OL,12,Fhim to arrive.
OL,14,FSarah said when she first raised
OL,15,Fconcerns to management at the nursery,
OL,16,Fshe was told that they were
OL,17,Finvestigating Bennett's behaviour and
OL,18,Fhad spoken to him directly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
