OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FFor her it seemed like the issue had
OL,13,Fbeen resolved. She didn't hear from
OL,14,Fthe nursery again. So to then hear of
OL,15,FBennett's arrest was difficult to
OL,16,Fdigest.
OL,18,FSarah said: "Despite the fact I had
OL,19,Fmade a complaint, I still didn't ever
OL,20,Fthink it was going on, and I was
OL,21,Fcompletely horrified.
OL,26,@zD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
