OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773756670
OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"I mean horrified on behalf of my
OL,8,Fchild who was under Nathan's care for
OL,9,Ffive months and because my child had
OL,10,Falready left the nursery by that point
OL,11,F- and there was no CCTV going back
OL,12,Fthat last couple of months - so we
OL,13,Fwill never know exactly what happened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
