CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773756670
OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"We will never know what was happening
OL,8,Fin that room for those five months so
OL,9,Fthat is horrifying and I will worry
OL,10,Fabout that every day of my life - and
OL,11,FI also am horrified on behalf of all
OL,12,Fof the children who we know were
OL,13,Fvictims - who've had to go through
OL,14,Fthat abuse."
OL,16,FBennett is guilty of 21 sexual
OL,17,Foffences against five children.
OL,19,FHe was only caught because parents
OL,20,Fraised their concerns motivating
OL,21,Fmanagement to look into it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
