OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FSarah said: "The nature of the crimes
OL,8,Fwas extremely predatory towards
OL,9,Fextremely vulnerable children. When I
OL,10,Fsay vulnerable children, all children
OL,11,Fare vulnerable in that they aren't
OL,12,Fparticularly verbal, they have innate
OL,13,Ftrust in their caregivers, and that
OL,14,Fwas blown apart by what he did.
OL,26,@oD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
