OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"I think personally an important
OL,8,Fmessage is for all parents - for
OL,9,Fanyone who's looking after your
OL,10,Fchildren - to really be a strong
OL,11,Fadvocate for your child to ask about
OL,12,Fsafeguarding policies for anyone who's
OL,13,Flooking after your children when
OL,14,Fyou're not there to trust your gut
OL,15,Finstincts to speak up and to push for
OL,16,Fanswers."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
