OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FIn a statement today a spokesperson
OL,8,Ffor Partou Kings Street Nursery said:
OL,9,F"In the year since these offences
OL,10,Ffirst came to light, we have worked
OL,11,Fwith a number of individuals and
OL,12,Forganisations to consider any ways in
OL,13,Fwhich we could strengthen our
OL,14,Fsafeguarding of the children in our
OL,15,Fcare.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
