OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773756670
OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"We have acted upon recommendations
OL,8,Fand as a result have increased
OL,9,Ftraining provided about safeguarding,
OL,10,Fstrengthened policies, including with
OL,11,Fregard to recruitment and
OL,12,Fwhistleblowing, increased the number
OL,13,Fof personnel in our leadership team
OL,14,Fwho focus on safeguarding and
OL,15,Fintroduced more internal and external
OL,16,Fauditing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
