OL,3,C'Horrified': Mother who complained
OL,4,Cabout paedophile nursery worker speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"We have also committed to expanding
OL,8,Fthe use of CCTV across the Partou
OL,9,Festate. We are in consultation with
OL,10,Fother sector stakeholders and
OL,11,Fgovernment to support initiatives that
OL,12,Fstrengthen safeguarding across the
OL,13,Fsector."
